extendedInfo.description: Check functional video at: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z3baIu8Tw18Impact T9 Dialer widget provides an easy way to dial phone numbers instantly,It supports T9 contact search right at your phone's homescreen.To place the widget on your homescreen, long press and choose widgets from the menu, pick Impact T9 Dialer widget from the widget picker screen and you are good to go.Upcoming release will feature stunning skins and more features. All the upcoming releases will be free for users who have already bought the widgetNOW INCLUDES CALL LOGSsupported for android 2.2+ONLY ENGLISH LANGUAGE IS SUPPORTED..PLEASE DO NOT ADD REVIEWS IF YOU WANT IT FOR ANOTHER LANGUAGENEW ANGRY BIRDS THEMEif you have any query/trouble using it please contact us at contact@impact-works.com

reviews.title: Almost no customizability!!
reviews.comment: Every view looks like it was made for a 12 tear old girl. Also, despite the fact that I looks compact it takes up the whole page and so cannot be used with other apps or widgets. I kno it only costs a dollar but I would buy a coffee instead. Is there a rating lower than  star!?!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Very poor interface
reviews.comment: I really expected this to be good. Extremely poor widget with bad keyboard alignment for a dialer. Do not download its a waste of money
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Shame
reviews.comment: Like the default look of the free version but i want a dialer to look like a dialer, not 5 numers accross 2 down.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: The t9 search doesn\'t work,can\'t resize widget thus making it too small. Lastly,  all of the different skins should have 3 column dialers. Oh yea is there a settings button? I tried to change the skin but couldn\'t. Only way I was able to change the skin was by erasing the widget and then put it back on my screen very annoying.  Please fix!!
reviews.author: amad robinson
